title: NEW YEAR, NEW YOU (2018) - A Think Story Takedown
author: Think Story
comment: I’m sorry! When the girl kicked the other girl in the stomach, it was hilarious. Yes, I don’t care enough to remember their names.

I wish they used the mirrors for something instead of the character just looking at every mirror. I was thinking it would symbolize that Alexis is trapped, and when she kills Danielle, she would punch a mirror, again symbolizing she's not trapped anymore. And THEY NEVER explain how Alexis got her scar (or maybe they did and I don't remember). I really thought this movie was going to be good but it just turned out kinda bad
I thought this was a really great video and you should definitely do more takedowns I like how you just basically obliterated the entire show!
This movie had like no plot it felt stupidly aimless?? Youre like the only person I’ve seen react to this garbage, bless you for suffering through it to please Totally Tubular 🙏
description:
In my new series we take a look at Hulu's fourth installment of its "Into the Dark" series with "New Year, New You." If your resolution was to watch more bad horror this year, boy do we have a good one for you!
